{"tid":2079031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"富臨集團控股(01443.HK)預計年度盈轉虧至6億-6.5億港元","createTime":"2020-06-25T13:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T13:29:47.000Z","uid":274167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b32e3dc1a539cce2826ebdc3d8dc3713b1b208e2","tid":2079031,"uid":274167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"06-24 22:49<br />\n<br />\n格隆匯 6 月 24日丨富臨集團控股(<a href=\"http://01443.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01443.HK&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=04711569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01443.HK</a>)公佈，預計集團於截至2020年3月31日止年度將<span style=\"color: red;\">錄得虧損約6億港元至6.5億港元(而去年同期則錄得溢利2550萬港元)。</span><br />\n<br />\n主要歸因於：(a)集團的收益較截至2019年3月31日止年度減少介乎26%至32%；(b)集團於2020年財政年度錄得虧損的餐館的物業、廠房及設備、使用權資產、商譽以及無形資產的減值虧損以及貿易應收款項的減值虧損合共約2.5億港元；及(c)其他因素，如投資物業的公平值虧損、撇銷其他應收款項以及金融資產的公平值虧損。<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gelonghui.com/news/370261?lang=hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gelonghui.com%2Fnews%2F370261%3Flang%3Dhk&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=3d646de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gelonghui.com/news/370261?lang=hk</a>"},{"pid":"e6c2b80e48913c53221af788cd66944a852a03e2","tid":2079031,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"もつどもつど<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}